<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 20:08:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队在加沙地带南部哈马斯枢纽汗尤尼斯市发起地面行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-initiates-ground-operation-in-khan-yunis-hamas-hub-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018c-3ae3-d11b-a3bf-feeb33320000</link><description>哈马斯高级人物和许多总部都位于汗尤尼斯，据估计，这里是该组织在加沙地带的部队指挥地。以色列国防军一名高级指挥官表示，过去24小时的战斗是“战争开始以来最激烈的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 19:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-initiates-ground-operation-in-khan-yunis-hamas-hub-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018c-3ae3-d11b-a3bf-feeb33320000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质告诉内塔尼亚胡的战时内阁，哈马斯扣押的俘虏遭受饥饿和性侵犯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-tell-war-cabinet-that-hamas-held-captives-suffered-hunger-sexual-assault/0000018c-3abd-dc03-a9ec-3efff69c0000</link><description>获释的人质参加了会议，分享了有关哈马斯对待俘虏的严厉证词。然而，他们的主要批评是针对政府的：“感觉是你根本不知道那里发生了什么。”你声称有情报，但事实是我们正在被轰炸”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 19:33:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-tell-war-cabinet-that-hamas-held-captives-suffered-hunger-sexual-assault/0000018c-3abd-dc03-a9ec-3efff69c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军法院因未对被枪杀的以色列平民进行尸检而怀疑士兵的定罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/court-doubts-soldiers-conviction-due-to-missing-autopsy-of-fatally-shot-israeli-civilian/0000018c-3a80-dc03-a9ec-3efb65860000</link><description>一名以色列陆军法官延长了对阿维亚德·弗里贾的拘留期限，他被指控犯有鲁莽杀人罪，预计将被释放并软禁。法官表示，他认为嫌疑人的行为是非法的，但这样做是由于“无心之失”，他认为以色列受害者是恐怖分子</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 18:40:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/court-doubts-soldiers-conviction-due-to-missing-autopsy-of-fatally-shot-israeli-civilian/0000018c-3a80-dc03-a9ec-3efb65860000</guid></item><item><title>美国对在西岸针对巴勒斯坦平民实施暴力的以色列定居者实施签证禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/u-s-imposes-visa-ban-on-israeli-settlers-engaged-in-violence-against-w-bank-palestinians/0000018c-3b10-d5f2-a5cc-7f14eb790000</link><description>预计相关定居者的名字不会被公开，这表明美国官员希望利用此举的私人性质——这是美国数十年来对以色列采取的最严厉的惩罚措施——作为未来制裁的威慑和威胁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 18:08:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/u-s-imposes-visa-ban-on-israeli-settlers-engaged-in-violence-against-w-bank-palestinians/0000018c-3b10-d5f2-a5cc-7f14eb790000</guid></item><item><title>“我们不能强行进入”：红十字会直面以色列人质事件的愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-05/ty-article-podcast/we-cant-force-our-way-in-the-red-cross-confronts-israeli-anger-over-hostages/0000018c-3a54-d5f2-a5cc-7e54eeb50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 17:19:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-05/ty-article-podcast/we-cant-force-our-way-in-the-red-cross-confronts-israeli-anger-over-hostages/0000018c-3a54-d5f2-a5cc-7e54eeb50000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗将美国拖入间接冲突，却没有为此付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-managed-to-draw-the-u-s-into-an-indirect-conflict-without-paying-a-price-for-it/0000018c-3a61-d11b-a3bf-fee9cfad0000</link><description>德黑兰将其军事反应限制在“独立”代理人的战略使其具有否认性，即使没有人相信，也可能成为阻止美国对其发动攻击的因素。矛盾的是，华盛顿很乐意接受这一主张，以避免更广泛的地区战争</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 16:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-managed-to-draw-the-u-s-into-an-indirect-conflict-without-paying-a-price-for-it/0000018c-3a61-d11b-a3bf-fee9cfad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方批准极右翼游行集会，要求“犹太人完全控制”圣殿山</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-far-right-plans-to-march-on-temple-mount-demand-end-of-waqf-control-of-compound/0000018c-3a3c-d11b-a3bf-febdfd150000</link><description>这次游行计划在光明节前夕举行，被称为“马卡比游行”，以纪念古代犹太人的叛乱。哈马斯领导人哈尼亚将 10 月 7 日的“阿克萨洪水”袭击与犹太人在圣地的存在联系起来</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 15:26:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-far-right-plans-to-march-on-temple-mount-demand-end-of-waqf-control-of-compound/0000018c-3a3c-d11b-a3bf-febdfd150000</guid></item><item><title>假婴儿，真正的恐怖：加沙战争的 Deepfake 增加了人们对人工智能误导能力的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/deepfakes-from-the-gaza-war-increase-fears-about-ais-power-to-mislead/0000018c-3a07-dc03-a9ec-3e7fadf10000</link><description>社交媒体帐户正在利用人工智能传播有关以色列-加沙战争的错误信息，专家担心这对冲突的未来意味着什么</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 13:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/deepfakes-from-the-gaza-war-increase-fears-about-ais-power-to-mislead/0000018c-3a07-dc03-a9ec-3e7fadf10000</guid></item><item><title>尽管以色列情报部门警告哈马斯可能发动袭击，但军队并未撤离诺瓦节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/despite-intel-warnings-about-a-hamas-attack-the-army-didnt-evacuate-the-nova-festival/0000018c-3993-dc03-a9ec-3dfb2cda0000</link><description>10 月 7 日前一天晚上，高级国防官员就哈马斯可能发动的袭击举行了紧急磋商。但以色列国防军中没有人通知新星节组织者或参加聚会的人，数百人被砍倒——在九个小时的时间里，没有人来拯救他们</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 13:41:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/despite-intel-warnings-about-a-hamas-attack-the-army-didnt-evacuate-the-nova-festival/0000018c-3993-dc03-a9ec-3dfb2cda0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯 10 月 7 日发射火箭，引发据称装有核导弹的以色列基地起火：《纽约时报》报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/hamas-rockets-on-oct-7-spark-fire-near-nuclear-capable-rocket-storage-facility/0000018c-39ea-dc03-a9ec-3dfb70980000</link><description>以色列对其核能力维持战略模糊政策。以色列中部的斯多特米查基地于 10 月 7 日遭受火箭弹袭击，严重受损，该基地部署有以色列可携带核弹头的杰里科导弹</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 13:19:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/hamas-rockets-on-oct-7-spark-fire-near-nuclear-capable-rocket-storage-facility/0000018c-39ea-dc03-a9ec-3dfb70980000</guid></item><item><title>美国顶尖大学校长将因对校园反犹太主义的反应而受到国会盘问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/heads-of-top-u-s-universities-to-be-grilled-by-congress-over-response-to-antisemitism/0000018c-3995-dc03-a9ec-3dff193b0000</link><description>哈佛大学、麻省理工学院和宾夕法尼亚大学校长将于周二出席听证会，要求校园领导负起责任并对抗反犹太主义</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 11:39:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/heads-of-top-u-s-universities-to-be-grilled-by-congress-over-response-to-antisemitism/0000018c-3995-dc03-a9ec-3dff193b0000</guid></item><item><title>周一，五名以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-monday-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-3966-dc03-a9ec-3d7fe0ab0000</link><description>周二早些时候，以色列国防军宣布三名士兵被杀，但后来又公布了周一被杀的另外两名士兵的名字</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 11:02:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/five-israeli-soldiers-killed-monday-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-3966-dc03-a9ec-3d7fe0ab0000</guid></item><item><title>照片中的 2023 年：极端气候</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/year-end/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/2023-in-photos-extreme-climate/0000018c-39a3-d5f2-a5cc-7fb7ca920000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 11:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/year-end/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/2023-in-photos-extreme-climate/0000018c-39a3-d5f2-a5cc-7fb7ca920000</guid></item><item><title>母女乌干达之旅成为犹太人的反思</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-mother-daughter-trip-to-uganda-becomes-a-reflection-on-being-a-jew/0000018c-3926-d11b-a3bf-ffaf237e0000</link><description>纪录片《谁像你一样？》中非洲阿巴尤达亚社区之旅产生了意想不到的结果– 在耶路撒冷即将举行的犹太电影周上放映</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 10:59:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-mother-daughter-trip-to-uganda-becomes-a-reflection-on-being-a-jew/0000018c-3926-d11b-a3bf-ffaf237e0000</guid></item><item><title>德国和奥地利主要评论员抨击联合国未能解决哈马斯针对妇女的罪行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/german-austrian-commentators-slam-toothless-un-over-failure-to-address-hamas-crimes/0000018c-395d-de12-a3af-3bddf4d80000</link><description>巴黎恐怖袭击引发人们对伊斯兰原教旨主义抬头的担忧，德国媒体试图追究联合国未能解决针对以色列妇女的性暴力问题的责任</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 10:52:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/german-austrian-commentators-slam-toothless-un-over-failure-to-address-hamas-crimes/0000018c-395d-de12-a3af-3bddf4d80000</guid></item><item><title>报告称，哈马斯可能在 10 月 7 日袭击之前使用间谍侦察以色列国防军基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/hamas-may-have-used-spy-to-scout-idf-base-before-oct-7-attack-report-says/0000018c-3980-de12-a3af-3bcdbc260000</link><description>根据战斗后恢复的地图，一名以色列官员告诉《卫报》，文件中发现的详细程度暗示了该设施的“内部知识”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 10:42:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/hamas-may-have-used-spy-to-scout-idf-base-before-oct-7-attack-report-says/0000018c-3980-de12-a3af-3bcdbc260000</guid></item><item><title>报告称，以色列正在讨论使用海水淹没加沙隧道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/israel-debating-using-seawater-to-flood-gaza-tunnels-report-says/0000018c-3909-dc03-a9ec-3d7b120a0000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，以色列为此目的组装了一个大型水泵系统，并于上个月向美国提交了该计划。埃及过去曾成功地利用海水淹没加沙隧道，但由于所有人的目光都集中在以色列，一些人对后果和国际反应表示担忧</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:42:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/israel-debating-using-seawater-to-flood-gaza-tunnels-report-says/0000018c-3909-dc03-a9ec-3d7b120a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡腐败审判的法官接受因战争而减少听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/judges-in-netanyahu-corruption-trial-accept-reduction-of-hearings-due-to-war/0000018c-393d-d11b-a3bf-ffbd56ee0000</link><description>审判的最后一次听证会于 9 月举行，此后法庭因节日休庭。 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击后，整个法院系统暂停了除紧急案件外的所有诉讼程序，包括对总理的审判</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:26:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/judges-in-netanyahu-corruption-trial-accept-reduction-of-hearings-due-to-war/0000018c-393d-d11b-a3bf-ffbd56ee0000</guid></item><item><title>强奸作为战争武器：犹太妇女呼吁联合国对抗哈马斯的性暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-and-jewish-women-implore-a-reticent-un-to-confront-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-369b-dc03-a9ec-3efbfcb90000</link><description>经过备受批评的沉默之后，联合国召开了首次特别会议，讨论 10 月 7 日大屠杀期间“有预谋和有计划”使用性暴力的问题。发言者包括希拉里·克林顿、谢丽尔·桑德伯格和以色列官员，他们介绍了迄今为止收集到的证据</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-and-jewish-women-implore-a-reticent-un-to-confront-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-369b-dc03-a9ec-3efbfcb90000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯被释放的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/the-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity/0000018c-0fb3-d65f-a7dd-fff736090000</link><description>100 多名以色列人和外国人质于 10 月 7 日在加沙被绑架后已获释或获救。这份确认的名单将不断更新</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 08:51:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2023-12-05/ty-article-magazine/the-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity/0000018c-0fb3-d65f-a7dd-fff736090000</guid></item></channel></rss>